[I apologise for the repetition but it took some time for the accounts to
settle down into a consistent pattern. There seems to have been contact but
not infection. One may wonder why the package was "damp" after travelling
for a month. If this is bioterrorism and not a mere imitator, it is a
significant difference in strategy to target low profile individuals in
other countries. The true Atlanta poster must know the families concerned
and is probably known by them. - Mod.MHJ
